---
title: Teriyaki Beef & Mushroom Rice Bowl with Veggies & Sesame Dressing
description: Centre yourself and relax with a bowl of teriyaki-flavoured beef mince. The mushrooms really lend an earthy taste that’s too good to be true. So sit back and enjoy this easy-to-make dinner with no fuss and a lot of flavour.
